    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 1.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_04-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "うわ～、広いお家だね～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow‚ this house is so spacious.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.2666666666666666,
      "endTime": 5.989886585871378,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 6.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_04-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "ここはうちの家族が所有する別荘やから\n自由にくつろいでくれてええよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This here's my family's holiday villa.\nFeel free to kick back and take it easy 'round these parts.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.2,
      "endTime": 12,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 12.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_04-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "リゾート地の別荘……\nおしゃれな内装……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A holiday villa in a resort area…\nStylish decor…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.2,
      "endTime": 15.899999999999999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 16.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_04-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "優はセレブ感をあまり出さないから忘れがちだけど\nお父さんは社長でお母さんは大女優なのよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You don’t act much like a celebrity‚ Yu‚ so it’s easy to forget‚\nbut your dad’s a company president‚ and your mom’s a famous actress.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.1,
      "endTime": 23.666666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 23.866666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_04-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "そんなにたいしたことあらへんよ\nみんな忙しくてここもあんま使ってへんしなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It ain't no big deal‚ really.\nWe're all mighty busy‚ so we don't use this place much.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.866666666666667,
      "endTime": 29.966666666666665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 30.166666666666668
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_04-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "優ちゃんに言われた通りステージ衣装を持って来たけど\nここで何をするつもりなの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I brought the stage outfits‚ like you said‚ Yu-chan‚\nbut what are we going to do here?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.166666666666668,
      "endTime": 37.233333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 37.43333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_04-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "この別荘にはダンスルームがあるから\nライブのリハーサルしてもらおう思て",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Our holiday home's got a dance room‚\nso I reckon y'all could rehearse the show in there.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.43333333333333,
      "endTime": 42.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 43.03333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_04-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "でも、このまま雨が降り続けたら明日のライブは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But if it carries on raining like this‚ tomorrow’s live…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.03333333333333,
      "endTime": 47.733333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 47.93333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_04-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さん、表情が硬いわ\nもっと肩の力を抜いた方がええんとちゃいますか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko-san‚ you're all stiff as a board.\nMaybe y'all should relax and loosen up a tad.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.93333333333333,
      "endTime": 54.333333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 54.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_04-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "ねえ優ちゃん、リハーサルを始める前に\nお家の中を見学してもいいかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey Yu-chan‚ before we start the rehearsal‚\nhow about you show us around the house?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.5,
      "endTime": 60.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 60.63333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_04-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "優ちゃんの別荘……興味津々……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m really curious to see Yu-chan’s holiday villa…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.63333333333333,
      "endTime": 63.733333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 63.86666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_04-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん好きに見てくれてええよ\n遙子さんも、ぜひ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If y'all wanna snoop 'round‚ go right ahead.\nHaruko-san‚ come tag along with us too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.86666666666667,
      "endTime": 68.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 68.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_04-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "今はそんな気分じゃ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t feel like it now…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.7,
      "endTime": 70.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 71.13333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_04-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さん、見て\nインテリアが凄くおしゃれ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko-san‚ look.\nThe decors are so stylish.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.13333333333334,
      "endTime": 75.76666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 75.96666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_04-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "インテリアもいろいろあるわね、高級そうな壺とか\n大理石の灰皿とか、トロフィーとか置物とか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There are all kinds of decor. Classy vases and stuff.\nMarble ash trays‚ trophies‚ ornaments…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.96666666666667,
      "endTime": 86.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 86.23333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_04-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "全部鈍器……\nサスペンスドラマなら間違いなく犯行現場……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "All blunt weapons…\nIf this was a thriller‚ this would be the scene of the crime…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.23333333333333,
      "endTime": 92.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 92.23333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_04-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "雫ちゃん！？\nインテリアを鈍器って呼ぶのはどうなのかしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shizuku-chan?!\nYou shouldn’t call decors “blunt weapons.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.23333333333333,
      "endTime": 97.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 97.66666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_04-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "絨毯もソファもふかふか！\n横になったら気持ちよく寝られそう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The carpet and the sofa are so fluffy!\nIf I lay down there I could sleep so comfortably…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.66666666666667,
      "endTime": 103.73333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 103.93333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_04-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "さくらちゃん！？\n寝るならベッドで、ね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura-chan?!\nIf you’re going to sleep‚ wouldn’t a bed be better?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.93333333333334,
      "endTime": 107.20000000000002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_yuvillaliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 107.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_04-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "お金持ちといえば剥製……\n鹿とか熊とか虎とかないのかな……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Being rich and having mounted animals go hand in hand…\nDeer and bears and tigers‚ do you have them here?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.4,
      "endTime": 113.5000001118101,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_04-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "実家にはあるけど別荘にはないなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There's some of them in the main house‚ but not here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.7,
      "endTime": 117.33333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_04-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "実家にはあるのね……！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ you have some in the main house…?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.53333333333332,
      "endTime": 119.26666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
