      "text": "全員で入れるくらい広いし、窓からは海が見えるんよ\n沖縄の海を眺めながら入るお風呂は格別やで？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Big enough for everyone to squeeze in‚ with a view of the sea from the window.\nTakin' a bath while gazin' out at the Okinawan sea is somethin' special.",
